quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,98,"Shichila shina nilulabaho olukongo olwasuubila kho obusubili balwo bubakhonye, halali abandu ba Yunus? Olwa basuubila, khwabarusiliaho eshinyasio shiokhututuyia mubulamu bwokhushialo mana nikhubahelesia omwikhoyo khubise (bia khwenya)."
  10,99,"Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yenyanga, abandu boosi bali khushialo bakhasuubile. Kho nawe wakhanichilisia abandu mbu khobabe Abasuubili?"
  10,100,"Ne abulaho omundu unyala okhusuubila halali khukhuchama khwa Nyasaye. Ne akholanga eshinyasio shibe khubalia abalarumishilanga amachesi kabu tawe."
  10,101,"Boola mbu; “Lole ni shina shili mwikulu nende khushialo.” Ne ebimanyisio nende amekanyilisio shibikhonyanga abandu balasuubila tawe."
  10,102,"Koo, bakhalindanga elindi halali akafwanana nende aketsinyanga tsia bandu babura imbeli wabu. Boola mbu; “Mana liinde, ne siesi toto endi halala ninanyu mubalindanga.”"
  10,103,"Mana khulihonokosia Abarumwa befu nende balia basuubila ninabo. Ne endio ni lwa kakwanila okhuhonokosia Abasuubili."
  10,104,"Boola mbu; “Enywe abandu! Ni muli nende obukanakani khudini yanje, esie shelamanga ebia mulaamanga habundu wa Nyasaye tawe, halali elaamanga Nyasaye ulia ulibafwisia, ne enomesibwe mbu embe mubasuubili.""
  10,105,"Ne henjia obulayi obweni bubwo khu Idini niwitswenulile Nyasaye, ne olakhatema waba mubatsokaasinjia Nyasaye tawe."
  10,106,"Ne olalaama ebilali Nyasaye tawe, bilakhukhoonya nohomba okhukhuwumisia tawe. Ne nokhola orio, toto olaba mubandu ababii."